name: VoxOps AI
long_description:
Regulated industries like banking and insurance not only have huge, expensive and operationally cumbersome call centres, they need to make sure that they stay compliant to avoid huge fines. 

VoxOps uses AI to automate 80% of their inbound and outbound calls, ensure they adhere to relevant regulations and far exceed current industry best practices. All for a fraction of their current cost base.
